<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘶嘶嘶”卡阿的声音把猴子们吓得四处逃散。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些猴子从来没见过卡阿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他们都听说过关于可怕蟒蛇的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他能像长苔藓一样悄无声息地沿着树枝溜走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子逃跑时，巴鲁安心地松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和猴子们大战后，他觉得全身酸痛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉也受伤了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹爬出了蓄水池，甩了甩他湿乎乎的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那些猴子再进攻以前，我们去接毛克利吧。”巴希拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这儿时，他们不会再进攻的！”卡阿嘶了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子在哪儿呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这里！”毛克利在圆顶里跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被困了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把这孩子从这里弄出去。”毛克利脚边的蛇说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会踩到我们孩子的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“退后，毛克利。”卡阿命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟒蛇仔细地看了看圆顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，他发现大理石上有一条裂缝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，蟒蛇高高地抬起身体，不停地撞击大理石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”当大理石在一团尘土中破碎时，巴希拉惊叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利跳出来，扑到了巴鲁和巴希拉怀里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没事儿吧？”巴鲁问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我又疼又饿。”毛克利回答道，“但我很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿盯着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，你就是那个人类孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么你看起来像只猴子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利鞠躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您救了我的命和我朋友们的命。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”卡阿温柔地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，月亮已经落山了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们躲在石墙后面，不停地发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿爬进露台中央，啪地一声闭上了嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们吓坏了，看着他慢慢跳起舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的舞蹈，叫做‘卡阿的饥饿’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坐着别动，看着我！”蛇命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿左右移动他的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把身体围成圆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鳞片沙沙作响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利站在巴鲁和巴希拉身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看猴子们，又看了看朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都好奇地看着蟒蛇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿嘶嘶地说：“靠近点儿，猴子们......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们无助地摇摇晃晃向前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁和巴希拉也开始向前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利朝朋友们扑过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快！”他边拽朋友们边喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们离开这里吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这两只巨兽一惊，好像毛克利刚把他们从梦中叫醒一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们逃到稍微远一点的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉回头看了一眼蛇，吓得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不只是猴子们害怕卡阿。那条蛇也让我紧张。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁抖了抖毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“事情很顺利。我们又找到了毛克利。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，但这次小冒险让我们付出了代价。”巴希拉严肃地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们俩都受伤了，这会让我们几天没法打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，我们不得不求卡阿帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他瞪着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们警告过你，跟猴子们玩儿很愚蠢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利低下了头。“对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他太年轻了。”巴鲁说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他知道自己错了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“破坏规则时，作为惩罚，道歉是不够的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，他轻轻拍了几下毛克利的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”巴希拉说，“行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>根据森林法则，一次惩罚能解决所有问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>关于毛克利和猴子的错误，没必要再多说什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跳到我背上来，小兄弟。”巴希拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”毛克利爬到巴希拉背上，把头靠在了上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>